page.title: 18HOME LIFE.
page.content: In 1985 {40 children}from Monk Fryston school voted that the {following foods}were their{favourites. Cows milk, Oranges, Mandarin oranges, Penguin biscuits, Scrambled eggs, Ice cream, Fish cooked at fish shop, Minced meat, Buns, Rice Krispies, Frosties, Crisps, Cauliflower, Sliced white bread, Lettuce,Chicken, Tea, Lemonade. The{foods}that were{least {liked}were Dried milk, Gooseberries, Apricots, Plums, Breakaway biscuits, Scotch eggs, Liqourice sweets, Sponge cake, Cubs, Smash, Onions, Granary bread, Green peppers, Start,Stewed meat, Hot Ribena, Orange and Grape fruit drink.
